data.description: This Los Osos single-level residence features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, just waiting to be customized to your liking. The property is within close proximity to schools—Los Osos Middle School and Baywood Elementary. Not to mention within a mile drive to grocery stores, coffee shops, or the famous High St. Deli! Positioned on a corner lot, complete with RV parking, a spacious entrance gate, and a fully fenced backyard featuring a patio, this home offers ample space for all your recreational equipment and entertaining needs. Hang up some string lights, plant a small garden, and fill your backyard with peace or fun parties! The fully finished two-car garage is a notable highlight. Upon stepping inside, you'll be welcomed by the generous living room, accentuated by a wood-burning fireplace. Adjacent to this space is the complete "U-shaped" kitchen, offering abundant cabinetry and a sliding door for convenient access to the backyard. The bedrooms are thoughtfully situated down the hallway, each featuring unique sizes. The Master bedroom impresses with its spaciousness, including a large walk-in closet, an en-suite bathroom, and private access to the backyard. The secondary bedroom, which we could also call the second master, also has a private bathroom and access to the backyard. The residence includes newer windows and sliders, a new water heater, an upgraded 200 amp electrical system, enhanced water service of 1", and a 12-panel FULLY OWNED solar power system. High electric bills? Not here!! Don't miss the chance to experience this property firsthand—schedule a private showing today!
